properties.description: A warm space to access advice for those aged 11-25; Access free advice, hot and cold drinks, food and a safe space. Our Warm Space is stocked with hot and cold drinks, snacks and warm winter items. We play music, you can get creative with some mindful colouring. If you want advice or support, just speak to reception or any MAP staff. We’re there to help! We know we cannot solve this financial crisis and mental health emergency ourselves, but we can build something powerful and positive – together. No-one should be cold and on their own, so come and visit our Warm Space today.
